## System requirements

### Software

The code was developed and tested using:

* R version 4.4.3

### Operating system

Tested on:

* Rocky Linux 8.10 (Open OnDemand HPC environment)

### Hardware requirements

No specialized hardware is required. Large-scale single-cell analyses may benefit from access to a high-memory computing environment.

### Main R package dependencies

* Seurat (v5.5.0)
* SeuratObject (v5.4.0)
* harmony (v2.0.2)
* ggplot2 (v4.0.3)
* dplyr (v1.2.1)
* tidyr (v1.3.2)
* patchwork (v1.3.2)
* cowplot (v1.2.0)
* ComplexHeatmap (v2.22.0)
* circlize (v0.4.18)
* ggpubr (v0.6.3)
* ggrepel (v0.9.8)
* pheatmap (v1.0.13)
* SingleCellExperiment (v1.28.1)
* scuttle (v1.16.0)
* limma (v3.62.2)
* edgeR (v4.4.2)
